1 与 STUDIO-STRUCT-021\",","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":1555,"content":"    : path.join(__dirname, \"studio-v2-layering-baseline.json\");","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":1559,"content":"      \"Studio V2 客户端分层存量违规（STRUCT-021～024）。内容哈希不变则豁免；触碰文件必须改合规后移出本表。\",","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false},{"lineNumber":1575,"content":"  if (args.includes(\"--write-layering-baseline\")) {","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]},{"file":"scripts/studio-quality/structure-gate-config.json","matches":[{"lineNumber":40,"content":"  \"layeringBaselinePath\": \"scripts/studio-quality/studio-v2-layering-baseline.json\",","contentTruncated":false,"isContextLine":false}]}],"totalLines":11,"totalMatchedLines":11,"clientTruncated":false,"ripgrepTruncated":false}}}}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-87c0ca0c-46a7-41aa-8083-a492835141e5-39\nfc_541487c7-f0c4-9db5-9e61-f0ce1de357c3_5","startedAtMs":"1784855516534","completedAtMs":"1784855516692"},"model_call_id":"d5f9e08f-e925-468e-aca1-0e1d7d8c7880-6-m7jd","session_id":"d077d01e-46bc-4c07-be60-b644d8d5fda5","timestamp_ms":1784855516631}
{"type":"tool_call","subtype":"completed","call_id":"call-87c0ca0c-46a7-41aa-8083-a492835141e5-40\nfc_541487c7-f0c4-9db5-9e61-f0ce1de357c3_6","tool_call":{"readToolCall":{"args":{"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/09-Studio-V2前端目录结构与落点规则.md","offset":90,"limit":50},"result":{"success":{"content":"### 4.1 pageComponents\n\n`src/pageComponents/` 放页面主组件、页面私有组件、页面私有 hooks 和页面样式。\n\n目录按 `app/` 路由分类：\n\n```text\nsrc/pageComponents/\n  home/\n    index.tsx\n    index.scss\n    com/\n    hooks/\n  stories/\n    index.tsx\n    index.scss\n    com/\n    hooks/\n  debugger/\n    index.tsx\n    index.scss\n    com/\n    hooks/\n```\n\n规则：\n\n- `index.tsx` 是该页面主组件，不是 barrel。\n- `index.scss` 是该页面主样式。\n- `com/` 放页面私有展示组件。\n- `hooks/` 放页面私有 hooks。\n- 页面私有组件不得被其它页面直接 import。\n- 多页面复用的展示组件必须进入 `src/commonUiComponents/`（见 §4.5）；单页私有组件仍放本页 `com/`。\n\n### 4.2 bis\n\n`src/bis/` 放页面和组件背后的业务编排层。\n\n它不是 UI 展示层，也不是类型目录。它负责把用户动作、请求、store、mock 或后续 BFF 能力组织成页面可消费的状态和命令。\n\n分层真源：[技术设计 21](../../../技术设计文档/21-Studio客户端分层.md) · [studio-v2-client-layering.mdc](../../../../../.cursor/rules/studio-v2-client-layering.mdc)。\n\n```text\nsrc/bis/\n  shellBis/\n    packages/packages.shell.bis.ts      # 页级灌 store；可 next/navigation\n    storyEditor/storyEditor.shell.bis.ts\n  pageBis/\n    packages/\n      listPackages.bis.ts               # feature：读 store / 命令 xhr","isEmpty":false,"exceededLimit":false,"totalLines":456,"fileSize":13628,"path":"/Users/bolbiao/workspace/airpc-engine/docs/AI和人类/sudioV2.0版本/需求/ui/09-Studio-V2前端目录结构与落点规则.md","readRange":{"startLine":90,"endLine":139},"relatedCursorRulePaths":[],"relatedCursorRules":[]}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"call-87c0ca0c-46a7-41aa-8083-a492835141e5-40\nfc_541487c7-f0c4-9db5-9e61-f0ce1de357c3_6","startedAtMs":"1784855516570","completedAtMs":"1784855516727"},"model_call_id":"d5f9e08f-e925-468e-aca1-0e1d7d8c7880-6-m7jd","session_id":"d077d01e-46bc-4c07-be60-b644d8d5fda5","timestamp_ms":1784855516682}
